AB=c,BC=a,AC=b
\dfrac{AB}{AC}=\dfrac{BD}{DC}\Longrightarrow BD=\dfrac{ac}{b+c},DC=\dfrac{ab}{b+c} 
AD^2=AB\cdot AC-BD\cdot DC=bc-\dfrac{a^2bc}{(b+c)^2}\Longrightarrow AD=\dfrac{\sqrt{bc(b^2+c^2-a^2+2bc)}}{b+c}
BM\cdot AD^2+DM\cdot AB^2=(BM+DM)\cdot AM^2+BM\cdot DM(BM+DM)
